{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"基线","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/baseline","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>基线</strong>是指欧洲和西亚文字排版中，用于在上面放置字符的一条假象的基准线。</p>\n<p>字符的降部比如 g 和 p 会向下超出基线，带弧形的会向上和向下扩展的字形（ <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Glyph\">Glyphs <small>(en-US)</small></a> ），比如 C 或 3 会略微向下超出基线。</p>\n<p>东亚文字没有基线，他们的字形放置在方盒子，没有升部和降部。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"学习更多","title":"学习更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本知识","title":"基本知识","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>维基百科上的基线 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Baseline_(typography)\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Baseline</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技术参考","title":"技术参考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>MDN 上的 CSS 盒对齐 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Box_Alignment#types_of_alignment\">CSS Box Alignment</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"学习更多","id":"学习更多"}],"summary":"基线是指欧洲和西亚文字排版中，用于在上面放置字符的一条假象的基准线。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Baseline","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Ligne de base","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Baseline (ベースライン)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Baseline","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/baseline","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/baseline/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/baseline","title":"基线"}],"pageTitle":"基线 - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}